casebody.data:
Michael HARTMAN, et al., petitioners,
v.
William G. MOORE, Jr. No. 13-103. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 7, 2013.

Case below, 704 F.3d 1003 .

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit denied.

THE CHIEF JUSTICE and Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
